{"tha-ap512:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap512:0.2":"Kanikaravagga ","tha-ap512:0.3":"10 Nalikeraphaladayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap512:1.1":"“Nagare bandhumatiya, ","tha-ap512:1.2":"aramiko aham tada; ","tha-ap512:1.3":"Addasam virajam buddham, ","tha-ap512:1.4":"gacchantam anilanjase. ","tha-ap512:2.1":"Nalikeraphalam gayha, ","tha-ap512:2.2":"buddhasetthassadasaham; ","tha-ap512:2.3":"Akase thitako santo, ","tha-ap512:2.4":"patigganhi mahayaso. ","tha-ap512:3.1":"Vittisanjanano mayham, ","tha-ap512:3.2":"ditthadhammasukhavaho; ","tha-ap512:3.3":"Phalam buddhassa datvana, ","tha-ap512:3.4":"vippasannena cetasa. ","tha-ap512:4.1":"Adhigacchim tada pitim, ","tha-ap512:4.2":"vipulanca sukhuttamam; ","tha-ap512:4.3":"Uppajjateva ratanam, ","tha-ap512:4.4":"nibbattassa tahim tahim. ","tha-ap512:5.1":"Ekanavutito kappe, ","tha-ap512:5.2":"yam phalam adadim tada; ","tha-ap512:5.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap512:5.4":"phaladanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap512:6.1":"Dibbacakkhu visuddham me, ","tha-ap512:6.2":"samadhikusalo aham; ","tha-ap512:6.3":"Abhinnaparamippatto, ","tha-ap512:6.4":"phaladanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap512:7.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap512:7.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap512:7.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap512:8.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap512:8.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap512:8.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap512:9.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap512:9.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap512:9.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap512:10.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma nalikeraphaladayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap512:11.1":"Nalikeraphaladayakattherassapadanam dasamam. ","tha-ap512:12.1":"Kanikaravaggo ekapannasamo. ","tha-ap512:13.1":"Tassuddanam ","tha-ap512:14.1":"Kanikarekapatta ca, ","tha-ap512:14.2":"kasumari tathavata; ","tha-ap512:14.3":"Padanca matulunganca, ","tha-ap512:14.4":"ajelimodameva ca. ","tha-ap512:15.1":"Talam tatha nalikeram, ","tha-ap512:15.2":"gathayo ganita viha; ","tha-ap512:15.3":"Ekam gathasatam hoti, ","tha-ap512:15.4":"unadhikavivajjitam. "}